":1233723,"uid":26013,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d25ab462a8747bdba8efd93aaeeac045c36a0d16","tid":1233723,"uid":242630,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"唔怪得尋晚半夜開始咁多分化撚浦曬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要用返5年前個招，大台，督灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進步下啦松泰！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:10:07.000Z","msg":"呢個世界當然唔會咁啱得咁橋啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢以前有個國王<br />\n由細到大都好叻<br />\n所以一直好自負<br />\n<br />\n咁佢咪一開始好強硬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己真係東方不敗<br />\n宜家搞到一發不可收拾啦<br />\n唯有聽下條PR TEAM講出嚟認死狗<br />\n等啲蟻民停一停之際<br />\n即刻派班三毛軍搞下分化<br />\n<br />\n你諗下得七百萬人嘅地方可以谷到二百萬人出嚟<br />\n有乜可能化解到<br />\n一係成個政權倒台<br />\n一係要你班人慢慢分化<br />\n最後個個心淡退出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n所以！！<br />\n一定要記得目標係咩！！！！！<br />\n徹消惡法<br />\n放哂以前嘅義士<br />\n追究黑警法律責任</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4b5cbe35b9a6d59a599618e015a95772009ea406","tid":1233723,"uid":130140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:19:14.000Z","msg":"見到三毛唔駛同佢係咁對話，你只會間接幫佢地推po<br />\n<br />\n各位要保持理智，諗清楚！<br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"22de14b2d2b0fc93db35b93356c4b7869bdbae73","tid":1233723,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T23:20:39.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課 - *CUP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2Flessons-from-the-yellow-vests%2F&d=sdtaPhne9yHE0zuhYC4X4XQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=ed55e6fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/06/14/lessons-from-the-yellow-vests/</a>"},{"pid":"cb1b29948de8759286dbca601a748e688f34b06b","tid":1233723,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":